snippet.title: Official UK PlayStation Magazine - Net Yaroze - Roller
snippet.description:
This is a video of the Net Yaroze game Roller, created by Matthew Verran.

It was featured on Official UK PlayStation Magazine's demo disc 108.

In the video I play through the first few levels of the game.
